# Whitelist: the build context only needs the serving code, static game data
# and exported models. Everything else (14 GB of raw data, wandb runs, ...)
# stays out so builds are fast.
*
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!src
!data/set16/static
!models/vit/vit.onnx
!models/cnn/cnn.onnx
!models/xgboost/xgboost.json
!models/xgboost/xgboost_features.json
src/**/__pycache__
